<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
  
  <div class="col-md-3">
    <h4>鹿児島ひとり時間へようこそ！</h4>
    <p class="pt-4">このサイトは鹿児島県内のおひとり様向けのカフェや喫茶店を厳選し、<br>
        心地よいひとときを共有するサイトです。</p>
    <p class="pt-1">会員でない方も投稿をご覧になれますが、<br>
       投稿やコメントをご利用の際には会員登録が必要になります。</p>
  </div>
  
  <!--スライドショー-->
    <div class="content-container container mx-auto col-md-9">
 
      <div class="slide">
        <div class="slide-item">
          <%= image_tag "sakurajima1.jpg", class: "slide-img img-fluid float-end", width: "900", height: "500" %>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-item">
          <%= image_tag "ice_coffee.jpg", class: "slide-img img-fluid float-end", width: "900", height: "500" %>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-item">
          <%= image_tag "sakurajima_shiroyama.jpg", class: "slide-img img-fluid float-end", width: "900", height: "500" %>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-item">
          <%= image_tag "kaimondake.jpg", class: "slide-img img-fluid float-end", width: "900", height: "500" %>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-item">
          <%= image_tag "cream_soda.jpg", class: "slide-img img-fluid float-end", width: "900", height: "500" %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

      <h4 class="font-weight-bold">新着投稿</h4>
        <div class="row">
          <% @posts_latest4.each do |post| %>
          <div class="col-3">
            <%= link_to post_path(post.id) ,style: "color: black;", data: {"turbolinks" => false} do %>
              <%= image_tag post.user.get_profile_image, size: "50x50", class:"mt-3 rounded-circle user-icon"; %>
              <%= post.user.name %>
              <% if post.images.attached? %>
                <%= image_tag post.images[0], class: "rounded", size:"200x150", style: "object-fit: cover;" %>
              <% else %>
                <%= image_tag('no_image.jpg', size: '200x150') %>
              <% end %>
              <p><%= post.shop_name %></p>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <div class="text-right font-weight-bold mt-2"><%= link_to "全ての投稿を見る", posts_path %></div>
      
  </div>
</div>

 <script>
      $(document).ready(function () {
      $('.slide-item').hide();
      $('.slide-item:first').show();

      setInterval(function () {
      var currentSlide = $('.slide-item:visible');
      var nextSlide = currentSlide.next('.slide-item');

      if (nextSlide.length === 0) {
      nextSlide = $('.slide-item:first');
      }

      currentSlide.fadeOut(500);
      nextSlide.fadeIn(500);
      }, 7000); // 7秒ごとにスライドを切り替え
     });
  </script>